{"tid":2297710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"母親為2000元出賣12歲女初夜玩3P 　少女慘遭3男性侵10餘次","createTime":"2020-11-23T12:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T20:23:17.000Z","uid":209657,"like":8,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"3eaeeb2cfd07c9819afa33adb5b8f6d1b1f2c4ec","tid":2297710,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/Tpbh5anMIJ-58dmCva8y3wZpJpw=/640x388/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6F4ABB6OIG6ZU2Y37KGAOP4N6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTpbh5anMIJ-58dmCva8y3wZpJpw%3D%2F640x388%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6F4ABB6OIG6ZU2Y37KGAOP4N6Q.jpg&h=4c66fcf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彰化一名少女3年前國小剛畢業，竟被母親以2000元將初夜賣給同村一名伯公，之後少女先後遭母親的同居男友陳男、楊男性侵共10次，其中3次母親甚至一起大玩3P，有次楊男用玉米形按摩棒等物摧殘少女，母親不忍，央求「別玩了」，反被楊男痛扁。<br />\n<br />\n最高法院今依違反《兒童及少年性剝削防制條例》等罪，判少女母親10年5月徒刑，伯公、楊男等3名男子各判刑1年8月到8年6月定讞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201123/ASR7EE36PRA3ZMGC4ZBLO5WMYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FASR7EE36PRA3ZMGC4ZBLO5WMYU%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=995976fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FASR7EE36PRA3ZMGC4ZBLO5WMYU%2F&h=8aaf5422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201123/ASR7EE36PRA3ZMGC4ZBLO5WMYU/</a>"},{"pid":"c889c4f1f0ae7667b63bc4762f1663406b5438bd","tid":2297710,"uid":5253,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"e856e8f3aad769257aea35b429238b0a2697628a","tid":2297710,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"5舊水"},{"pid":"0d620ec5e3abd46e91c48babeb9b7712161b637e","tid":2297710,"uid":282352,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"台灣加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727c4a1b3969b451f40112fa50ca27ae34868058","tid":2297710,"uid":330457,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"為咗$2000台幣個老母係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec76fe8f093ebbc29e9527b0c953c31d66bb514","tid":2297710,"uid":209657,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/kuTbOMesRmU4OLUeSY7AwOX-dpo=/510x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S4BSCII5MZ26AG45LO3FCO3PCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkuTbOMesRmU4OLUeSY7AwOX-dpo%3D%2F510x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS4BSCII5MZ26AG45LO3FCO3PCY.jpg&h=5d813b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n判決指出，被害少女與從事板模工的母親相依為命，家境不好，2017年6月，少女剛從國小畢業，有天母親帶她到同村一名熟識的林姓伯公家吃補品，母親抵達後卻藉故離開，她被伯公半摟半推進房內性侵得逞，事後伯公拿2000元給她，說是要借給母女當生活費。<br />\n<br />\n少女當時才12歲，失去童貞很驚嚇，但母親收下她轉交的錢，一句解釋都沒說，少女不敢向其他長輩求助，將秘密藏在心底，隔年（2018年）7月間，少女隨母親跟母親當時的34歲陳姓男友同住，有天陳男酒後卻向少女求歡，少女自認已非完璧、沒有拒絕，到隔年2月為止，共與陳男合意性交7次。"},{"pid":"41ab1d6773c6669ab438261663c30c32e8de4905","tid":2297710,"uid":203543,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"所以咪話，台灣真係一個充滿住bitch同厹既地方，呢個地方既人成個腦除左諗點樣恥笑香港叫支那之外，就係諗住做愛，sex，做愛，外遇，偷情，同人妻人夫做愛，亂倫， 強姦，迷姦，撿屍，一有時間就諗下可以點樣屌到自己個呀嫂，堂/表姐妹，女朋友/老婆嘅姊妹，或者朋友個女，朋友個孫，弱智信徒嘅弱智女、 弱智孫女，老闆屌女秘書，醫生屌女病人，偷嘢女客人主動叫處男店員屌佢同幫佢口交，老師就想同自己個學生做下愛咁，學生又諗下點屌個大波miss，再唔係就係最鍾意做愛果時拍下片，方便以後分手再要脅下個前度做多幾次分手愛，台妹最馨同條仔吵兩句嘴就馬上搵前度傾心事，傾傾下就又做愛，個前度問佢可唔可以內射，台妹搖頭說不，但最後還是被射滿滿，所以話，呢個地方真係十分淫亂。"},{"pi